readable.content: A man kneels on a dock while a dog jumps in the water next to him . A man on a narrow dock plays with his dog that is jumping out of the water . A woman kneeling on a dock throws a ball to a dog that is jumping in the water . A woman kneels at the edge of a dock reaching toward a dog leaping nearby in the water . Dog leaps from water while woman kneels on the dock playing with him
